What, exactly, did you predict?  That quote is in reference to Clinton's proposed mechanism for enforcing an individual mandate.  That has very little to do with the current topic or your claim in this thread, to wit: &quot;Once you have a UHC system in place, we’ll see innumerable polices just like [the proposed Mississippi bill] become law; cost pressure makes it inevitable.&quot;<br />
<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px; ">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
	<table cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
	<tr>
		<td class="alt2" style="border:1px inset">
			
