	</tr>
	</table>
</div>
<br />
Yet the <a href="http://www.lifeclinic.com/healthnews/article_view.asp?story=513218" target="_blank">single largest study ever done on the topic</a> does not support that view. Incidentally, the main scientific criticism of that study &#8212; that it's based on unreliable statistics that don't accurately track secondhand smoke patterns &#8212; also applies to the studies that purport to show a link between secondhand smoking and ill health. <br />
<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px; ">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
	<table cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
