		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
</div>
<br />
&quot;It bugs me&quot; is a bad reason to ban something. Flatulence and excessive perfume are stifling and invasive of my clean air space, but we still shouldn't ban them. The only scientifically valid reason for banning smoking is that smokers cost everyone money. And if that's reason enough for banning smoking (and for quite a few people it is), then it's certainly reason enough to ban food service to fatsos.
                  
		</div>
